      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark cases (lid-driven cavity, pipe flow) within published tolerances.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases. Internal verification reports confirm second-order spatial accuracy for velocity and pressure fields in laminar and turbulent regimes relevant to blood pump flows."
