      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares the same impeller topology and operating envelope as the COU device. Fluid properties (bovine blood) are physiologically representative. Operating points span the clinical CPB range. Validation scenario is judged highly relevant to the COU."
    },
