    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD predictions of the relative hemolysis index agree with in-vitro measurements within the ±15% acceptance criterion across all 5 operating points. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device submission.",
